net.sf.kdgcommons.test

Class ArrayAsserts

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.kdgcommons.test.ArrayAsserts

  • public class ArrayAsserts
extends Object
    Static methods for asserting array equality. Each method performs the following assertions:
    • actual array is not null
    • actual array has same size as expected array
    • each element in actual array is equal to corresponding element in expected array
